Hoyan Mok

Hoyan Mok (莫可欣)，was the winner of the 1993 Miss Hong Kong Pageant and a TVB Hong Kong actress. She beat Kenix Kwok, who was considered a favourite to win, having won two side awards including Media`s Favourite and Potential Artist.
